2. ADX — Average Directional Index             |
═══════════════════════════════════════════════
 
ADX answers ONE question:
    "Is the market trending or just bouncing around?"
 
It tells you: whether it is SAFE to trade mean reversion right now.
 
  ADX < 25  → Market is RANGING  → mean reversion is SAFE   ✅
  ADX ≥ 25  → Market is TRENDING → mean reversion is RISKY  ❌
 
ANALOGY:
  RANGING market = ping pong ball bouncing between walls → good for reversals
  TRENDING market = train moving in one direction → don't stand in front of it!
 
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
 
FORMULA:
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
 
Built in three steps from High, Low, Close prices:
 
  Step A — True Range (TR)
  ────────────────────────
  TR = max of:
    option 1 = High − Low              (today's candle)
    option 2 = |High − Previous Close| (gap UP overnight)
    option 3 = |Low  − Previous Close| (gap DOWN overnight)
 
  → TR captures the REAL daily move including overnight gaps.
 
  Step B — Directional Movement (+DM / -DM)
  ─────────────────────────────────────────
  up_move   = Today High − Yesterday High
  down_move = Yesterday Low − Today Low
 
  if up_move > down_move AND up_move > 0:
      +DM = up_move,  -DM = 0   ← upward day won
  elif down_move > up_move AND down_move > 0:
      -DM = down_move, +DM = 0  ← downward day won
  else:
      +DM = 0,  -DM = 0         ← no clear direction
 
  Step C — Smooth everything → +DI / -DI → DX → ADX
  ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  alpha = 1 / 14  (Wilder smoothing)
 
  smooth_TR   = ewm(TR,   alpha=1/14)
  smooth_+DM  = ewm(+DM,  alpha=1/14)
  smooth_-DM  = ewm(-DM,  alpha=1/14)
 
  +DI = 100 × smooth_+DM / smooth_TR   ← % of range that was upward
  -DI = 100 × smooth_-DM / smooth_TR   ← % of range that was downward
 
  DX  = 100 × |+DI − -DI| / |+DI + -DI|  ← how DIFFERENT are they?
 
  ADX = ewm(DX, alpha=1/14)                ← final smoothed trend strength
 
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

