  | ADX < 25     | ✅ YES | Market is RANGING → allow    |
  | ADX ≥ 25     | ❌ NO  | Market is TRENDING → block   |
 
  ADX = 18.0 → below 25 → market is ranging → entry ALLOWED ✅
 
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
