5. Weekly Trend Filter (WeeklyBull)            |
═══════════════════════════════════════════════
 
The weekly filter answers ONE question:
    "Is the big picture trend working with us or against us?"
 
It tells you: only trade mean reversion WITH the macro trend.
              Don't buy in a downtrend. Don't sell in an uptrend.
 
ANALOGY:
  Don't swim against the current. Trade WITH the big trend.
  A BUY signal in a falling market is a falling knife.
  A SELL signal in a rising market fights the tide.
 
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
 
FORMULA:
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
 
  WeeklySMA  = average of last 50 closing prices
 
  WeeklyBull = (Price_today > WeeklySMA)
                    ↑
              True  → long-term uptrend  → BUY allowed
              False → long-term downtrend → SELL allowed
 
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
 
