  Price today            = $107.50
 
  WeeklyBull = (107.50 > 102.00) = True  → long-term UPTREND
 
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
How it gates BUY and SELL:
 
  | Signal   | WeeklyBull | Decision              |
  | :------- | :--------- | :-------------------- |
  | BUY      | True       | ✅ ALLOW  (buying in uptrend)   |
  | BUY      | False      | ❌ BLOCK  (buying in downtrend) |
  | SELL     | False      | ✅ ALLOW  (selling in downtrend)|
  | SELL     | True       | ❌ BLOCK  (selling in uptrend)  |
 
