  | WeeklyBull  | True     |
  | BUY allowed | YES ✅   |
  | SELL allowed| NO ❌    |
 
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
GOLDEN RULE
 
  WeeklyBull = True  → uptrend  → BUY  ALLOWED,  SELL BLOCKED
  WeeklyBull = False → downtrend → SELL ALLOWED,  BUY  BLOCKED
 
  Always trade the oversold dip WITH the bigger trend.
 
