  | R:R ratio    |    2 : 1 |
 
══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
GOLDEN RULE
 
  ATR tells you HOW MUCH the stock moves.
  Bigger ATR → wider stop + bigger target (high volatility stock).
  Smaller ATR → tighter stop + smaller target (calm stock).
  The 2:1 reward-to-risk ratio is always maintained.
 
